      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for an experienced mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated project car. The engine struggles to remain operational, and the exterior shows significant wear, including rust and fading paint. It is being sold as-is, and I would recommend towing it from the lot as it is not currently reliable for daily driving.",
