    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly with no known mechanical issues, and the transmission shifts reliably through all gears. The interior is clean with only minor signs of regular use, and the exterior paint retains a healthy shine despite a few small, typical road chips. It is a dependable driver that is ready for the road immediately without needing any urgent repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
