    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable driver that's ready for its next chapter? This well-loved vehicle is in fair condition and still has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a functional and spirited ride at a great value. It's a solid performer that\u2019s eager to get back on the road with a new owner!",
      "price": 22000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
